				<div class="content-text">
                	<h3>Shelter</h3><br>
                    <img src="./images/shelter.jpg"/><br><br>
                    <p>The 25 acres of land will be divided into 150 plots covering 15-20 decimals. Entrepreneurs can purchase one or more plots according to their needs.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>In a city with limited entertainment options  shopping becomes a major recreational activities for the city dwellers. In this respect, Departmental stores in particular, where one can get a large variety of items under a single roof, has become a popular choice for the busy city dwellers harassed by time constraints.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        After years of pioneering efforts spent in developing the industrial and the commercial enterprises the Group has come to realize the potentialities of Bangladesh's property development sector. With overwhelming successes in the paper, knitwear and paper converting ventures, the Group has incorporated the Bangladesh Development Company Ltd. (BDC), to explore the real estate opportunities, which has ultimately become a milestone in the Group's expanding and diversified businesses. The housing comlexes are being developed for providing maximum facilities of modern life at optimum cost for the common people of Bangladesh.
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        East, West, North, South, New and Islami Towns are unique projects of BDC to meet the acute housing crisis by building satellite towns which will meet not only  needs but also provide all other facilities that are required for modern living. These towns will provide the desired housing facilities for about 0.10 million dwellers in seven localities. On providing all modern amenities and utilities like gas, electricity and water the land plots are made available at a very reasonable instalments. Apart from the residential accommodation the towns will also have public transportation system, which will link up the satellite towns with the mega city.
                    </p>
                </div>